{"title":"同献红心一片","authors":["周路石","祝天乔"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"同献红心一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周路石画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝天乔诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵锣鼓声喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人脸露笑颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车站人流似海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔赴农业前线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本在不同岗位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"业务各有所专，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今去到农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同献红心一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响应伟大号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去到农村锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投身三大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重担挑在双肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心改造思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要改造自然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场坚定不移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何畏险阻艰难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是青年工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾把技术苦练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下乡修理农具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助农业增产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是文工队员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜把英雄扮演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要演现代剧目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞人们向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩挑图书图片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻灯随带身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为农民服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤广作宣传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务虽各不同，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有共同心愿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为祖国农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力作出贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵锣鼓声喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍重道声再见；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮飞快滚动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前程无比灿烂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}